# Evolve rules with code

Trigger when patterns stabilize: unstated repeat shape, recurring bug/review, library becomes default, security/perf/test norm settled.

**How**: diff vs `.cursor/rules/ai-rules/`; one topic per file; examples from repo; cross-link, don't duplicate.

Format bar: [write-cursor-rules-for-this-project.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/ai-rules/rules-for-rules/write-cursor-rules-for-this-project.mdc)
